result.name: Thai Simple Kitchen

reviews.text:
Excellent place to eat original Thailandese food. The decoration was made with taste.
Bonus: an exterior terrace!
Good food, fast service and nice restaurant.  Conveniently located.
Awesome place we order a lot of food here and I have started liking there noodles and some Chicken and cashwes combinations even   Laksak soups are awesome.

I was told by my friend that this place never gets full even-though it's in CWB and it has a nice small rooftop area as well. It's better to share your food with friends because the portions are quite big. I accidentally spilled my drink that was half gone already and the waitress gave me a new one!
Food is good, environment is nice. Has both indoor and outdoor space. Price is reasonable.

result.name: 泰簡單

reviews.text: 有宵夜💃💃
好耐冇嚟過食lunch, 估唔到冇食一排水準又差左，本身個menu唔多選擇，叫左個炒牛肉粒，好韌，十粒有八粒都唔食得，已向侍應反映但一d反應都冇，我唔介意佢個set lunch貴多十幾廿蚊但比返好少少嘅肉人地食，除左係平同坐得舒服唔知有咩係好
香港銅鑼灣區很少有露天位，還可以分吸煙區及非吸區的泰國菜餐廳，環境都可以，食物都唔差。
0K。食物質素仍可保持。
